{
  "name": "Widen Area",
  "type": "feat",
  "effects": [],
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are wielding a weapon with the area or automatic trait.</p><hr /><p>You set up your area weapon to affect more targets. If the next action you use is to make an attack with a weapon that has an area of burst, cone, or line, increase the area of that attack. Add 5 feet to the radius of a burst that normally has a radius of at least 10 feet (a burst with a smaller radius is not affected). Add 5 feet to the length of a cone or line that is normally 15 feet long or smaller, and add 10 feet to the length of a larger cone or line.</p>"
